        "action": "Vehicle tax to include levy for repair of roads maintained by local authorities",
        "additional_details": "Evidence can be found in the budget of local authorities.  Requirements exceed funding, over many years, by large amounts.",
        "background": "The condition of local roads is poor.  Pot holes and bad repairs are a mounting problem that impact all road users.  The situation in places can be dangerous and cause significant costs.  A link to vehicle tax would be a link to the number of vehicles and thus provide proportionate funds.",
